{"lemma":"نَحْتُ","slug":"نَحْتُ","root":"ن.ح.ت","root_slug":"ن-ح-ت","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ح-ت","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n39473","n39474"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%92%D8%AA%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to carve (wood or stone), to sculpt, to shave, to plane, to smooth, to scratch, to saw off, to excavate (a rock)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to lie with","tags":["figuratively"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to emaciate a camel (toilsome journey)","tags":["figuratively"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to opprobriate, to chide","tags":["figuratively"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of نَحَتَ (naḥata) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"carving (carved object)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"compounding; univerbation, portmanteauing etc. of new words"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Inherited from Proto-Semitic *naḥat-."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n39473","headword_ar":"نَحَتَ","root":"nHt","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L, K,) contr. to analogy, (TA,) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,) which is the form preferred by IJ, because of the guttural letter, but this is disputed by MF, (TA,) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which is the form of weakest authority, (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHotN","text_ar":"نَحْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hewed; formed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fashioned, by cutting; cut out, hewed out,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shaped out; chipped:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraY","text_ar":"بَرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he worked"},{"kind":"text","text":"wood and the like"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as a carpenter;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najara","text_ar":"نَجَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":":"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he pared, peeled, barked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deprived of its outer covering"},{"kind":"text","text":"by"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"paring, abrasure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wearing away the exterior: he sawed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laHata","text_ar":"لَحَتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] Accord. to some, the operation termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nHt","text_ar":"نحت"},{"kind":"text","text":"is only performed upon something hard and strong, as stone and wood and the like. (MF.) [↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AntHt","text_ar":"انتحت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"seems to signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for himself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinotaHito mina Alxa$abi maA yakofiyka lilowaquwdi","text_ar":"اِنْتَحِتْ مِنَ الخَشَبِ مَا يَكْفِيكَ لِلْوَقُودِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Cut,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hew, for thyself, of the wood, what will suffice thee for fuel"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (A.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHata bayotFA fiY Aljabali","text_ar":"نَحَتَ بَيْتًا فِى الجَبَلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHotN","text_ar":"نَحْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut out,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hewed out, a house in the mountain."},{"kind":"text","text":"In the Kur, xv. 82, El-Hasan [El-Basree] reads"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yanoHatuwna","text_ar":"يَنْحَتُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) [Accord. to the K, his reading is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yanoHaAtuwna","text_ar":"يَنْحَاتُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tanoHaAtuwna","text_ar":"تَنْحَاتُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) but this I find nowhere else, and I believe it to be a mistake.] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuHita EalaY Alkarami","text_ar":"نُحِتَ عَلَى الكَرَمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was fashioned after the model of generosity; made by nature generous"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHata","text_ar":"نَحَتَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Inivit"},{"kind":"text","text":"puellam: (K:) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laHata","text_ar":"لَحَتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but the latter is the better known. (TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHata","text_ar":"نَحَتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHotN","text_ar":"نَحْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He beat, struck,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smote,"},{"kind":"text","text":"him with a staff, or stick: (TA:) [as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laHata","text_ar":"لَحَتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHata","text_ar":"نَحَتَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He threw"},{"kind":"text","text":"him"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"down prostrate."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHata bilisaAnihi","text_ar":"نَحَتَ بِلِسَانِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He blamed; reprehended; reviled"},{"kind":"text","text":"a man. (L.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laHata","text_ar":"لَحَتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHata","text_ar":"نَحَتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a journey, or travel,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"emaciated"},{"kind":"text","text":"a camel: (K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it made"},{"kind":"text","text":"a man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"less; made"},{"kind":"text","text":"him"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slender."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHata","text_ar":"نَحَتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"?] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHiytN","text_ar":"نَحِيتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHiytapN","text_ar":"نَحِيتَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sighed aloud:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the inf. ns. syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nay^iytN","text_ar":"نَيِيتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaHiyrN","text_ar":"زَحِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","L","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n39474","headword_ar":"نَحْتٌ","root":"nHt","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHaAtN","text_ar":"نَحَاتٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHiytapN","text_ar":"نَحِيتَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Nature; natural,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"native, disposition, temper,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other property;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a particular cast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fashion, of constitution, after which a man is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as it were"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut out"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the Creator"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) and the first, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"source,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"origin, from which one is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as it were"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut out:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[see also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manoHatN","text_ar":"مَنْحَتٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Lh.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkaramu mino naHotihi","text_ar":"الكَرَمُ مِنْ نَحْتِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Generosity is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a part"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of his nature;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"derived"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from his source."},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"origin."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hawu Eajiybu Aln~aHoti","text_ar":"هَوُ عَجِيبُ النَّحْتِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is of a wonderful nature."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hawu kariymu Aln~aHiytapi","text_ar":"هَوُ كَرِيمُ النَّحِيتَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is generous in nature,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disposition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barodN naHotN","text_ar":"بَرْدٌ نَحْتٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Unmixed"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sever"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cold:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) but this is said to be a corruption of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baHotN","text_ar":"بَحْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laHotN","text_ar":"لَحْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["K","S","TA"]}]}}